snippet: Jonas Valanciunas had 22 points and 11 rebounds for Toronto, which bounced back from consecutive losses. The Nets have not won at Barclays Center since Dec. 10.
abstract: NBA Roundup; Toronto Raptors defeat Brooklyn Nets, 91-74; other basketball scores noted.
